"represenging all major earthquakes. Download the `tab-delimited earthquake "
"data "
"<http://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/nndc/struts/results?type_0=Exact&query_0=$ID&t=101650&s=13&d=189&dfn=signif.txt>`_."
msgstr "Useremo il `Significant Earthquake Database <http://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/nndc/struts/form?t=101650&s=1&d=1>`_  come nostro layer di riferimento per rappresentare i principali terremoti. Scaricate il t`tab-delimited earthquake data <http://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/nndc/struts/results?type_0=Exact&query_0=$ID&t=101650&s=13&d=189&dfn=signif.txt>`_"

